---
title: Tropical Lemon Pepper Prawn Burger with Aioli & Veggie Fries
description: Not only are we cheering for our favourite teams to take home a win, but we’re also cheering for zesty pepper prawns to win over
our tastebuds. Go all out plating them up in a burger, slather in a tropical mango mayo and serve with crisp veggie fries. We think
it’s truly a win-win night.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
